👉🏻 @thepastatable for all things pasta!
All 🍕🍔🍝🍟🍹consumed by me
📷 by me

- Est. 2013 -

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Ruby's Murray Hill with @rubyscafe. May be an image of french fries.

node.text: FRYDAY 🍟🍟🍟 Best truffle fries in NYC! @rubyscafe #fries #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in New York, New York with @thepastatable. May be an image of food.

node.text: If you like pasta give my new account @thepastatable a follow! This is my “grown up” version of spaghettio’s - Anelli with vodka sauce & fresh mozz 📸 @thepastatable #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Morandi Restaurant with @morandinyc. May be an image of pasta.

node.text: Tagliatelle me baby, what’s your story? 🎶🍝 This Tagliatelle Bolognese from @morandinyc is 💯. The pasta is the perfect consistency and the sauce is full of flavor! #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Montesacro Pinseria Brooklyn with @montesacrobk. May be an image of pizza.

node.text: Sunday slice 🍕 Infernetto Pinsa with Fior di Latte Mozzarella, Tomato, Spicy Soppressata, Pecorino from @montesacrobk - if you haven’t tried pinsa before, it’s a super light, Roman-style pizza and the ones at @montesacrobk are incredible! They have a ton of options to choose from too! #pizza #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Alice Restaurant NYC with @alicerestaurantnyc. May be an image of food.

node.text: Agnolotti, we like to party, we don’t cause trouble we don’t bother nobody 🎶🍝Cacio e Pepe Agnolotti from @alicerestaurantnyc - this pasta is sooo soft and melt in your mouth delicious! #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NYCFoodComa • Jessica on August 11, 2021 tagging @lecreuset, and @dhamakanyc. May be an image of food.

node.text: Highlights from the @lecreuset Hot Dish pop-up dinner at the new @dhamakanyc to celebrate the launch of their newest color - Cayenne! The last night of the Hot Dish pop-up dinner is tonight (8/11) and you don’t want to miss it - such a fun experience trying all of these new and exciting dishes! #CasuallyColorful #ad #NYCFoodComa

node.text: Stacks on stacks on stacks 🍔Legendary Cheeseburger with  double, american cheese, kimchi mayo, b&b pickles from @nowon.nyc - this cheeseburger was amazing, definitely a top NYC burger! #burger #NYCFoodComa

node.text:
Had a blast at the #SeaportArtois event last week! The perfect spot to celebrate summer with great pizza, beer, music, views and vibes! Top chefs from some of the best NYC restaurants are serving up their best slices alongside @stellaartoisusa. Check out the link in my bio for a chance to win a table at one of the upcoming events! [ad] #NYCFoodComa 

#eeeeeats #eater #nyc #nyceats #nycfood #foodie #foodporn #forkyeah #insiderfood #infatuation #tastethisnext #buzzfeast #eatfamous #dailyfoodfeed #newforkcity #tastingtable #nyceeeeeats #food #beautifulcuisines #feedfeed #eaterny #timeoutnewyork

node.text: Always sonny ☀️ Finally made it to @sonnyboy_nyc - highlights include the rigatoni with Burrata, the burger, fig & Burrata toast and the chicken parm. The burger was amazing and definitely a must! #burger #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.text: Turning Taco Tuesday up a notch with the new @tacowaybeach x @caracasarepabar collab via the @doordash test kitchen! After struggling during the pandemic, these two restaurants teamed up with @doordash to bring a combined delivery & takeout service to Manhattan - you can order the former East Village  @caracasarepabar arepas and Rockaway Beach's @tacowaybeach tacos all at once for your next Taco Tuesday party or picnic! #ad #NYCFoodComa
